        <p data-role="text">Those who want to visit Sen&#xAD;tosa&#x2019;s Tan&#xAD;jong, Palawan and Siloso beaches from next week&#xAD;end can now book their slots on&#xAD;line. Safety mea&#xAD;sures have been put in place to min&#xAD;imise Covid-19 risks.</p>
